ges. The book points to the need for language learning materials to deal seriously with knowledge about the world, including its diversities and problems.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aCultural pluralism in textbooks. 0aLanguage and culture. 0aLanguage and languagesxTextbooksxEvaluation. 0aLanguage and languages-Textbooks-Evaluation. 0aMulticultural education. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aLanguage teaching materials.  aTextbook analysis.  acritical cultural awareness.  aculture in language learning.  aintercultural competence.  alanguage learning materials.  anational stereotypes.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishz978311060401608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060678240uhttps://doi.org/10.21832/978178309956640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781783099566423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781783099566/original  a978-3-11-060401-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics and Social Sciences 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060678-2  MultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb